The paper discusses the use of machine learning, including deep learning, for automatic acoustic detection of birds. This falls under the sub-category of Sound (cs.SD) in computer science. The paper also mentions the use of various machine learning techniques such as convolutional neural networks (cs.CV), support vector machines (cs.LG), and recurrent neural networks (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the evaluation of performance metrics (cs.AI) for the proposed methods.
